cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.IR 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with machine translation and language processing. It could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it uses unsupervised techniques and neural MT systems. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it uses neural networks for translation. Finally, it could also be classified under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as it deals with the retrieval of latent translations from rough glosses.
